        <div class="section">
            <h2>🌍 About This Ancient Wisdom</h2>
            <p>The Odu system comes from the sacred Ifá tradition of the Yoruba people, brought to Brazil and evolved through centuries of spiritual practice. Each of the 16 paths represents a unique archetypal pattern that influences how your soul navigates life.</p>
            <p>Your birth date contains the mathematical signature of your soul's chosen path. Through the sacred cross calculation, we reveal not just your main path, but the complete energetic blueprint of your consciousness.</p>
